Uses of Interface
com.github.tadukoo.view.lookandfeel.paintui.PaintUIResource

Packages that use PaintUIResource
Package Description
com.github.tadukoo.view.lookandfeel
Contains the TadukooLookAndFeel, which allows you to customize the Look & Feel more easily through the use of the TadukooTheme class and TadukooThemeFactory.
com.github.tadukoo.view.lookandfeel.paintui
Contains PaintUIResource and its implementations to allow for customizing the Paints to be used in TadukooLookAndFeel within the TadukooTheme.

    Classes in com.github.tadukoo.view.lookandfeel.paintui that implement PaintUIResource
    Modifier and Type Class Description
    class  ColorPaintUIResource
    ColorPaintUIResource is a PaintUIResource to be used in TadukooLookAndFeel for custom paints if you want a solid color.
    class  GradientUIResource
    GradientUIResource is simply a LinearGradient wrapped as a PaintUIResource so that it can be used in TadukooLookAndFeel by putting it in a TadukooTheme.
